</para>
<para id="element-30">
<list id="list-3" list-type="enumerated">

<item> Find the time when velocity is zero. </item>
<item> Does the velocity changes its direction? </item>
<item> Locate position of the particle in the successive seconds for first 3 seconds.
 </item>
<item> Find the displacement of the particle in first three seconds. </item>
<item> Find the distance of the particle in first three seconds. </item>
<item> Find the displacement of the particle when the velocity becomes zero.    </item>
<item> Determine, whether the particle is under constant or variable force. </item>
</list>
</para>



<para id="element-31">
