<solution id="idm180672">
<para id="element-606">  One of the particles begins with a constant velocity, “v” and continues to move with that velocity. The second particle starts with zero velocity and continues to move with a constant acceleration, “a”.  At a given instant, “t”, the first covers a linear distance,
</para>


<para id="element-607">
